# 🇪🇪 ShuddhiCheck AI – Phase II: Estonia Readiness

This folder contains the official readiness brief and rollout strategy for ShuddhiCheck AI’s Phase II expansion into Estonia.

📄 [Download Estonia Readiness Brief (PDF)](./ShuddhiCheckAI_PhaseII_Estonia_Readiness.pdf)

---

## 📌 Key Highlights

- GDPR enforcement via Estonian Data Protection Inspectorate (AKI)
- Advanced digital health stack: X-Road, DigiDoc, national EHR system
- Global leader in e-Government and blockchain-backed health records
- Innovation-friendly environment with English support for demos
- Estonian required for public rollout; Russian optional (localized use)

---

## 🏛️ Governance & Innovation Partners

- Ministry of Social Affairs – Estonia
- Estonian Data Protection Inspectorate (AKI)
- TEHIK – Health and Welfare Information Systems Centre
- Ministry of Economic Affairs and Communications
- Connected Health Cluster Estonia

---

## 🌐 Language & Localization

| Language   | Role |
|------------|------|
| **Estonian** | ✅ Required for dashboards and health compliance systems |
| **English**  | ✅ Used in demos, innovation programs, EU collaborations |
| **Russian**  | 🟡 Optional (regional use in northeast only) |

🟢 Demo kits in English and full rollout in Estonian supported.

---

## 🛠️ Next Steps

- Upload PDF readiness brief
- Reach out to TEHIK and Ministry of Social Affairs
- Begin pilot preparation for X-Road integration and dashboard localization
